        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 26 at 10:16PM MDT until July 26 at 10:45PM MDT by NWS Great Falls MT</headline>
        <description>At 1015 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 30 miles north of
Gildford, or 39 miles northwest of Havre, moving east at 45 mph.

HAZARD...Quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Damage to vehicles is expected.

This severe thunderstorm will remain over mainly rural areas of
northeastern Hill County.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
